    <title>NexT主题添加“返回顶部”和“返回底部”功能按钮</title>
    <url>/posts/4e9d51da.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>本方法基于Hexo8.1.2框架的NexT8.27.0主题，可能不适合其它框架或主题。<span id="more"></span></p>
<h3 id="操作方法"><a href="#操作方法" class="headerlink" title="操作方法"></a>操作方法</h3><p><strong>一、下载安装<code>hexo-cake-moon-menu</code>插件</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cake-moon-menu</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>二、添加文件并修改主题</strong></p>
<p>在<code>blog/_config.next.yml</code>文件中找到主题自带的<code>back2top</code>，将<code>enable</code>后面的<code>true</code>设置为<code>false</code>，然后添加下面的代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 自定义返回顶部 + 返回底部按钮</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">moon_menu</span>:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">back2top</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">icon</span>: fas fa-chevron-up</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">order</span>: -<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">back2bottom</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">icon</span>: fas fa-chevron-down</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">order</span>: -<span class="number">2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
